{"tid":235220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估地方）女同學借宿一宵，竟遭父親在弟弟面前性侵","createTime":"2017-05-08T23:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T00:35:06.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89e5df4eaebc50420fd49da959d97578ff9ea2f7","tid":235220,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:13:10.000Z","msg":"〔記者鄭淑婷／桃園報導〕桃園市高中女生小敏（化名），因為忘了帶鑰匙且家中無人而無法回家，只好到葉姓男同學家中借宿一晚，豈料當晚竟遭葉父闖入房間性侵，葉男非常不齒父親惡行，怒罵「人渣」、「禽獸」，與母親大義滅親報警，警方依妨害性自主罪嫌將34歲葉父移送法辦，檢方聲押獲准。<br />\n桃園檢警調查，小敏來自單親家庭，與爸爸相依為命，6日晚間她返家時發現忘記帶鑰匙，爸爸因為在外地工作而無法趕回，她只好向同校但不同班的葉男求助，葉男熱心地帶她回家借住一晚。<br />\n葉男家中除了父母還有2個年幼的弟弟，葉男特地讓出自己房間給小敏與6歲的弟弟一起睡，葉男則與7個月大的弟弟擠在隔壁倉庫。隔天凌晨，葉男被媽媽叫醒說：「你爸爸的拖鞋，怎麼會在你同學的房間門口，房門還反鎖？」葉男驚覺不對勁，趕緊到門外不停敲門，房內無人回應只好踹門，只見爸爸十分不悅地打開門，小敏蜷曲在床上啜泣。<br />\n怒罵人渣 與母揭惡行<br />\n小敏指控葉父趁她熟睡時闖進房間性侵；葉父矢口否認。葉男懊悔來不及阻止憾事發生，非常不齒爸爸的劣行，怒斥「人渣」、「禽獸」，還說不想再喊他爸爸了。葉母也氣得破口大罵，母子倆決定不姑息，報警逮捕他。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/paper/1100682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F1100682&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d235688\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F1100682&h=aa0fab29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/paper/1100682</a><br />\n香港真係又輸一分了"},{"pid":"d21206026f4ca62c2d483218947dbb270be940c6","tid":235220,"uid":104148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:14:39.000Z","msg":"桃園 1分"},{"pid":"c96612daf7d514ef2aabc72a7c720b66aff5b15b","tid":235220,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:15:58.000Z","msg":"新北市0-1桃園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce11e7403a9446ad56823bba09a4ab2b762c0e11","tid":235220,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:17:23.000Z","msg":"我都未食 讓俾細佬 你偷食？"},{"pid":"7303f93ddad133663a06d93a94824831f6aea041","tid":235220,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:20:53.000Z","msg":"真～借叔一蕭"},{"pid":"921882d2c50727269e8b2ba1a1c7b49a0341c46c","tid":235220,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:27:10.000Z","msg":"所以咪話 台灣真係一個充滿bitch同厹的地方....."},{"pid":"b5d9496b8df4dbd5df28e6b7c251d725cdcb098a","tid":235220,"uid":37933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:34:07.000Z","msg":"好撚似柚木N定情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8478bfbb2833c8642f0e47f49cf906536ae5fd2c","tid":235220,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚似柚木N定情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柚木N'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ad97b6f820459402833df8eada8a7fda84d99e","tid":235220,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:36:58.000Z","msg":"34歲父親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8391d4bfd25c3269dad785b49d8d4dafc6509a60","tid":235220,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>34歲父親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5368f07a6bc1f08a870781e8552e946d7a8a99f","tid":235220,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>34歲父親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n34-15=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b9036ca73e14cf3918e16826e045df554445f9","tid":235220,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc